      "writtenOn": "2018-09-24T18:11:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think a simple recipe should be simple, ala:\n\nsteps :\u003d []Step{\n  SimpleStep(\"echo hello world\"),\n  Step{\n    Cmd: \"say hi\",\n    Pwd: \"go/test_automation\",\n  },\n}\n\nc.Do(steps)",
      "revId": "8099fde41beff266a3d35f0ce31323713173c3fd",
