        "id": 5205
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-09-25T13:47:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agreed that we should support conditional flows also for complex recipes, but a simple recipe should be simple.\n\n\"branching (eg. if dir doesn\u0027t exist, run \"git clone\"), etc.\"\n\nI thought there\u0027d be a higher level \u0027step\u0027 that I would just pass the repo URL and a relative directory name and it would just do the right things to make sure it appeared there.",
      "parentUuid": "57a4f274_2d27eb88",
      "revId": "8099fde41beff266a3d35f0ce31323713173c3fd",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
